modName: Alysson preset for RaceMenu ( The sister of Aela the Hunteress )
summary: This is a Preset in .jslot for RaceMenu. Alysson is my new characters. It's the Aela sister. If this preset has a good succès, i can make the unique follower, Alysson, the sister of Aela th hunteress. I hope that this character will please you and that you will make him to me understand !
descriptionHtml:
[url=http://imagesia.com/alysson-banner_yiit][/url][center][url=http://imagesia.com/alysson-banner_yiit][/url][url=http://imagesia.com/alysson-banner_yiit][img]http://img.imagesia.com/fichiers/yi/alysson-banner_imagesia-com_yiit_large.png[/img][/url][/center]

[img]http://i19.servimg.com/u/f19/16/46/20/79/infos10.png[/img]

[font=Comic Sans MS]This is a preset of my new characters, for [u]RaceMenu[/u].
[/font][font=Comic Sans MS]
Alysson is the sister of Aela, back in Skyrim after two years. 
You can make many Builds or RP's with, or play this redhair person as a simply Nordic' !

If you have any proposition, report, bug or other, you can write me.
[i]I'm beforehand sorry,  i'm not to moddeur, i have no big knowledge, just a passionate player.


[img]http://i19.servimg.com/u/f19/16/46/20/79/requir10.png[/img][/i]
This file is for [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url]. I also advise to you [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?]S[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?]howRaceMenu Precache Killer[/url] ( if you run Racemenu version 2.7 or higher you don't need ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer as it's integrated ).


[i][img]http://i19.servimg.com/u/f19/16/46/20/79/instal10.png[/img][/i]

For install this preset and can select him in the RaceMenu presets, put the .jslot in : Data\skse\plugins\CharGen\Presets.


[/font][img]http://i19.servimg.com/u/f19/16/46/20/79/mods10.png[/img]
I use for this preset and result :

- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]( CBBE ) Calientes Beautiful Bodies Edition[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/256/?tab=2&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D256&pUp=1]Detailed Bodies[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/689/?]Detailed Lips[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/498/?]High Quality Eyes[/url]
- [url=http://robton.nu/kshairdos/]K[/url][url=http://robton.nu/kshairdos/]S Hairdo's[/url] ( Hair cut )

I've add Tatoo's :

- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30404/?tab=2&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D30404&pUp=1]THEHAG's Private Tatoo[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41210/?tab=2&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D41210&pUp=1]THEHAG's Private Wartattoos -Facial Waraints for Females[/url]
- [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/62639/?]Empyrean Warpaints - Custom Series ( Females )[/url]


[img]http://i19.servimg.com/u/f19/16/46/20/79/notes10.png[/img]

You can worked again in this Preset with you're RaceMenu, in particular with the tool of sculpture.

If you have a bug ( or not ) with the haircut, you can change this for a new haircut, it's up to you, i propose only a basic model.
If you're Character has the blue foot, it's not a texture bug. See the foot colors in RaceMenu, you can have a color applicate.

[i]In my personnals screens, i've use the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6983/?]Dynasty White Armor[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11543/?]Crainte Vomir[/url].[/i]

If you add screens of what you will have made of this preset, i would be satisfied.
If you want to encourage me and to help me, endorsements will show a little my work and i you will be grateful for it!

/!\ Because i'm a beginner in Modding, i need help by an expert for make a ECE and CharGen files, NMM files, and their test. Please, write i.
